= CentOS + Apache + FastCGI =

* Install packages 

 yum install mod_fastcgi python-flup Django

* Init script ./fcgi-packageporter

Taken from http://www.question-defense.com/2009/12/30/init-script-to-run-django-fastcgi-threaded-on-a-tcp-port 

Pid file stored in ~/.packageporter/

* Apache conf ./packageporter.conf

Apache needs permissions to find files in static/ folder 
